#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/mail/_index.adoc:975
msgid ""
"The default directory opened by alpine is [.filename]#inbox#.  To view the "
"message index, press kbd:[I], or select the [.guimenuitem]#MESSAGE INDEX# "
"option shown below:"
